Nigerian Electricity Price to Increase 18% From July 1, Guardian Reports

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-06-24T08:08:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-24/nigerian-electricity-price-to-increase-18-from-july-1-guardian-reports.html
Nigerian electricity prices will
increase to 10 naira per kilowatt hour from 8.5 naira on July 1,
the Lagos-based Guardian newspaper reported, citing the Nigerian
Electricity Regulatory Commission.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gordon Bell at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  